<PB N="194" REF="219">
Altar. 4. The Altar. 5. The Holy Place in which the Bea&s;ts are &s;lain. 6. The Place in which they are burnt. 7. and 8.8, 8. The Stone-wall wherewith it is encompa&s;s'd.</P>
