<P>Let us &s;uppo&s;e then that the Paper is the Mountain, on the top of it is built an Altar to the Sun, and in a Place a little below that, is built one to the Moon, and in a Place yet lower, there is one to the 10 Stars.</P>
<P>Thus the People did punctually obey the Commands of our God, and his Orders as to Religious Wor&s;hip, are &s;trictly ob&s;erv'd to this very Day.</P>
